title: The Dead Trennedys 2/1: Snow and Panda, Marilyn Manson, Wakanda Disney+, Myanmar, Nike Hands-Free Shoes
itunes:title: The Dead Trennedys 2/1: Snow and Panda, Marilyn Manson, Wakanda Disney+, Myanmar, Nike Hands-Free Shoes
description:
On this edition of The Dead Trennedys Jack and DJ Danl discuss the panda who is LOVING the snow, Evan Rachel Wood revealing the years of abuse she received from Marilyn Manson, Ryan Coogler is developing a Wakanda series for Disney+, the Military of Myanmar has staged a bloodless coup, and Nike releases news shoes that are made to slip on, hands free!
